<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV70">
<l>vaḷaivāyt tiruccak karatteṅkaḷ vāṉava ṉārmuṭimē</l>
<l>ṟaḷaivāy naṟuṅkaṇṇit taṇṇan tuḻāykkuvaṇ ṇampayalai</l>
<l>viḷaivāṉ mikavantu nāḷtiṅka ḷāṇṭūḻi niṟkavemmai</l>
<l>yuḷaivāṉ pukuntitu vōrkaṅku lāyira mūḻikaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>So as to last for days, months, years, aeons, coming fast in order to ripen</l>
<l>[our] pallor of complexion for the cool Tulsi in the fragrant chaplet</l>
<l>with tight [bud] mouths on the full crown of our heavenly man with a curved, sharp,</l>
<l>splendid discus, this one night, entering  in order to torment us, is a thousand aeons.</l>
<l></l>
<l>b: pukuntitu</l>
<l>the night, a thousand aeons, is one that has entered in order to torment us...</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
